The <strong><code>WebGLSampler</code></strong> interface is part of the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API">WebGL 2</a> API and stores sampling parameters for <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLTexture" title="The WebGLTexture interface is part of the WebGL API and represents an opaque texture object providing storage and state for texturing operations."><code>WebGLTexture</code></a> access inside of a shader.